review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2021
name: S. Dalrymple-Ely
title: Good veggie sneaking but high sugar
review: These are good, I've tried them before giving them to my toddler. You can't taste the veggies at all, in any of the flavors. Reason why: the second ingredient is sugar. Good source of calcium and vitamins, just make sure you know the sugar content.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2020
name: Willie V. Hughes
title: Stonyfield Organic To The Rescue
review: When you need to run out the door and you want to bring a wholesome, filling snack for your toddler or kid, this is just the ticket. My toddler son loves these, and I like them because they are easy from him to sip from without spilling (e.g. in the car). I need to help him with the last bit by rolling the tube up, but I don't mind.
